@startuml
title Benchmark Usage Flow

start
:Generate raw benchmark data\n(gen_zero_shot.py);
:Export tokenizer views\n(export_views.py);
:Validate view consistency\n(validate_views.py);
:Build model-ready cases\n(build_model_io_json.py);
:Run model\n(run_api_model_list.py or run_ollama_model_list.py);
:Write predictions.jsonl;
:Evaluate with eval_predictions.py;
:Annotate with annotate_model_outputs.py;
:Review overall.json / by_task.json / by_tokenizer.json;
:Review cases_with_outputs.json / summary.json;
stop

@enduml
